race.comment: EL FORTRESS (1) settled towards the tail then wound up strongly to finish 1.1 lengths away in second when resuming last start over 1100m at this track. Rates among the top chances. SHOOTINGOFFTHEHAND (2) finished fourth last time out over 1100m here following a minor placing at this circuit when fresh from a spell the run prior. Right in this contest. RED CITY SUN (4) was beaten just a head last start when fresh from a spell and landed his first top-three finish in the process at Townsville over 1000m. Makes plenty of appeal on the back of that latest effort. MAYOR OF KINGSTON (3) turned in a decent effort last start to finish third over 1540m at Gold Coast Poly. Has his share of talent and will prove hard to beat in this suitable race.
